Package org.hibernate.boot

Interface Metadata

All Superinterfaces:
MappingContext
All Known Subinterfaces:
InFlightMetadataCollector, MetadataImplementor
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDelegatingMetadata, InFlightMetadataCollectorImpl, MetadataImpl
public interface Metadata extends MappingContext
Represents the ORM model as determined by aggregating the provided mapping sources. An instance may be obtained by calling MetadataSources.buildMetadata().
Since:
5.0
